<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1483922-why-is-the-first-book-i-ve-read-with">Why is the first book I&#39;ve read with missing pages? It stinks that when I am getting to...what seems like EVERY good part... a page or two is blank so I have to guess what happens. And I bought the book. Thanks.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1483922'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F39904267-true-places">like</a></span>

